comments: Snell (DET) and Porter Jr. (CHI) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Carter Jr. (CHI) makes contact to Rose's (CHI) body during his driving shot attempt.
Rose (CHI) makes contact to Satoransky's (CHI) body during the drive that affects his SQBR.
Satoransky (CHI) takes more than two steps after he has gathered the ball.
Drummond (DET) makes marginal contact with LaVine (CHI) during the rebound that does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Carter Jr. (CHI) makes incidental contact with Drummond's (DET) lower body during the rebound.
Drummond (DET) cleanly blocks LaVine's (CHI) driving shot attempt.
Porter Jr. (CHI) makes incidental contact to Snell's (DET) hand after the shot has been released that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Morris (DET) commits a take foul on Carter Jr. (CHI).
Drummond (DET) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Satoransky (CHI).
Rose (DET) commits a take foul on LaVine (CHI).
Drummond (DET) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Porter Jr. (CHI).
Drummond (DET) takes two legal steps after his gather.
Young (CHI) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Brown (DET).
Snell (DET) commits a take foul on LaVine (CHI).
Rose (DET) fumbles the pass initially and then legally regains possession of the ball.
